   <text>
      <body>
         <div>
            <l>‘<persName corresp="../metadonnees/IndexPersonnages.xml#PERSEPHONE">i</persName> wasn’t afraid,
               <persName corresp="../metadonnees/IndexPersonnages.xml#DEMETER">mama</persName>; </l>
            <l>i was bored. i was hungry.</l>
         </div>
         <div>
            <l>do you know how long i waited </l>
            <l>for that fruit? me in the fields, </l>
            <l>the sunlight on my hair a crown. </l>
            <l>sweat on my palms glittering </l>
            <l>like starbursts carved in marble, </l>
            <l>teeth sharp as athena’s sword. </l>
            <l><persName corresp="../metadonnees/IndexPersonnages.xml#HADES">he</persName> took one look at me </l>
            <l>and broke the earth open</l>
            <l>for desire. </l>
         </div>
         <div>
            <l>and all that time, you thought </l>
            <l>golden-armoured braggarts </l>
            <l>could storm my heart into </l>
            <l>surrender. oh, mama. </l>
            <l>what did I care to be a bride </l>
            <l>when i could be a queen? </l>
         </div>
         <div>
            <l>i wasn’t afraid, mama: </l>
            <l>i wasn’t taken. i left. </l>
            <l>if only you knew </l>
            <l>how his hair is softest </l>
            <l>when he’s on his knees, </l>
            <l>coaxing spring </l>
            <l>from inside of me.’</l>
         </div>
      </body>
